# Ci React Native xem Appium (Phn 1 - Cng tm hiu cch hot ng ca Appium)

2021-01-04 13 min read
react-native e2e-testing appium
Table of Contents
  • Mt vi kin thc cn c
  • Hardware
  • V d trn lm g?
  • Phn tch mt vi note v c php

1. M u

Do dng i a y v khch th tin t nhng li thch ht hng thm (ton i 80~100 coverage -_-) nn mnh cng kinh qua react-native-testing-library mt thi gian kha kh, v cng nghch th Detox, nhng cha thng no lm mnh hi lng:

  • Testing-library: Khi test e2e th phi mock qu nhiu, kh kh mock component sao cho hot ng ging nh component tht. C nhng lc mnh ch vit cho % coverage ln ch cc fn ca test b mock ht, thnh ra ch c ngha g nhiu. Cc thnh phn UI b mock ht, nn test pass m vn cht l iu bnh thng nh cn ng hp sa.
  • Detox: chi vi mi simulator, device tht ko r ti gi c nh in t cha.

V gn y th mnh c li docs ca React Native c recommend thm 1 thng - Appium. Appium s dng driver nh XCUITest, UIAutomator, Espresso, c cc teito (tay to :v) native cng ty bo my thng driver trn ton l hng hn bn native dng chy test, nn th nghch lun. Sau mt thi gian my m th kh hi lng.

Ti sao li dng Appium m ko chy cm cho khe?

Ni th ch thc ra th chy cm khng h khe t no u cc bn.

Khi ta pht trin 1 feature mi cho app, ta phi test cho c nhng tnh nng c, nh hng ti chng l iu kh trnh khi.

Thng thng dev chng ta s ngh l C tester ri xon g ng khng no? Tuy nhin phn dev qun th cng vn phi check qua nhng case c bn, (test thm case d cng tt) trc khi chuyn qua cho tester. Nhng khng l c vit mt feature l ngi bt app ln bm tng nt, cha k xe p mi ( mnh c mt ngi bn rt hay nhm newbie v newbike =)) ) newbie khng nm r h thng, lack case l iu tt nhin, hn na con ngi chng ta khng gii trong nhng vic nhm chn c tnh lp li cao nh test app, v vy d c l b lo th cng s c lc nhm ln.

Ngoi ra, cun The Effective Engineer ca Edmond Lau (nu ko c g sai st th l trang 159) c vit:

If you have to do something manually more than twice, then write a tool for the third time

Vy th sao chng ta khng my lm nhng cng vic nhm chn nh test, v focus vo nhng vic khin ta hng th hn. Hy cng hc vit test t ng cho ng dng React Native ca chng ta thi no!

Mt vi kin thc cn c

  • React Native, Babel (khng cn qu mt t)
  • Nm c c bn v vit unit test (vi jest, hay g tng t)
  • Typescript (optional): do bi vit s dng Typescript

Hardware

  • My Mac/Hackintosh build iOS hoc my Win (ch chy c Android thi)
  • 1 con in thoi iOS hoc Android - ni khng vi integration test trn simulator :v

2. Chy th v d nh

T dng nhi mt ng l thuyt sung, trong khi khng bit mnh s lm g c phi rt chn khng no? V vy trc tin ta hy chy th mt v d nh sau trc : ng k account

V d sau dng Typescript + WebdriverIO, v c cu trc tng ng vi v d trn trang ch ca Appium link (Cc bn cng c th vo link trn bng truy cp trang ch Appium ri bm vo nt Examples), tt nhin go pro th ta s ko code nh vy, mnh s thc hin refactor v chuyn i mi trng chy test cc bi sau ( nu c =)) ).

Sau khi setup Babel cng vi Jest (do Jest lun i km vi React Native nn mnh dng lun demo cho thn thin), hy vit 1 on test n gin cho qu trnh sign up ca ta. Hin ti mnh ch fill nhng field text input, v field select, date picker vit kh di, nn mnh s cp sau.

Ni nhiu qu, code u?

Vng, code y ( di c gii thch code)

Chi tit source code c th xem ti y

Source code ca cc mn hnh c th xem ti y:

  • Login screen link
  • Registration screen link

V y l thnh phm:

iOSAndroid

V d trn lm g?

  1. T mn Login, bm vo button Create an account login/toRegistrationScreenButton vo mn Registration

  2. Ti mn Registration

    1.1.Bm vo nt Registerregistration/registerButton, do my Android ca mnh mn hi ngn, nn trc khi click phi scroll ti element trc.

    1.2. Do cha fill g nn expect error message hin th tng ng

    1.3. Fill user..01vo input username, do field ny ch nhn alphabet v s, nn gi tr ko hp l, expect hin th error message

    1.4. Fill username 1 gi tr hp l user

    1.5. Fill password password

    1.6. Fill password confirmationpassword123, do ko match password nhp nn s hin th error

    1.7. Fill password confirmation hp l password

    1.8. Fill full name

    1.9. Bm vo nt Register

  3. User c chuyn qua mn RegistrationCompleted, nn ta expect button mn ny c hin th.

Phn tch mt vi note v c php

C php ca WebdriverIO nhn kh trong sng v d hiu, nn mnh s khng gii thch nhiu, tuy nhin c mt vi ch di y cho cc bn.

  • Khi tm element, mnh dng ~, y l shorthand tm element theo accessibility id ca WebdriverIO, tu theo OS m ta s phi gn prop khc nhau c th dng c strategy tm theo accessibility id ny link, ch v ci ny m mnh mt vi ting, ko hiu ti sao ko tm thy element =))

    • bn iOS ta phi dng testID, v trnh gn accessibilityLabel v accessibilityHint cho component.
    • bn Android, hy dng accessibilityLabel
    • Cc bn c th tham kho cc strategy khc docs ca webdriverio link

  • Ti sao li dng accessibility id m khng dng content ca n?

    • ng ra l khi bm button hay thao tc trn mn hnh, chng ta nn dng text ca n, khi text (requirement) thay i th test cng ong. Nhng m c bn l do hi bn li =)) v trng hp accessibility id ng nhng text sai th phi chp nhn thi =))

  • Do API ca WebdriverIO ton tr v Promise, nn hu nh cu lnh no cng cn phi dng async/await, cc bn c th s dng km package @wdio/sync API ca WebdriverIO tr nn ng b.

  • Cc bn c on code beforeEach v afterEach khng? Mi test, chng ta ang to ra mt session mi, v xo session sau mi test. Nu dng CLI ca wdio th s thun tin hn.

  • Options xcodeOrgId v xcodeSigningId bn trong capabilities ca RemoteOptions iOS

    • chy test trn thit b iOS, Appium s ci mt phn mm tn l WebDriverAgent ln thit b, v ci t c, ta phi cung cp developer team v signing certificate.

      Cc bn c th xem thm ti y link

  • i vi thit b tht th ta cn thm UUID, c th xem cch tm UUID ti y

  • capabilities ca Android

    • ly deviceName, hy chy adb devices

    • com.learnrne2etest v .MainActivity c th ly t android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml

      Hoc tham kho bi sau link

Ci nga xem hoa nh vy ri, chng ta hy cng tm hiu thm v cch hot ng ca Appium

3. Kin trc, flow ca Appium

Appium da trn kin trc client-server, bn thn Appium l 1 server, c th d dng nhn thy iu ny on config.

3.1. Test library + WebDriver client

Khi vit test, ta s dnh phn ln thi gian lm vic vi chng, nh v d phn 2, ta s dng Jest (vi cc cu lnh it, describe, afterEach, afterAll) l cng c chy test, v WebdriverIO (vi $, click(), setValue(value)) giao tip vi Appium server.

Ngoi b i ny, chng ta c th s dng bt c ngn ng no m ta thch (min l Appium n support :v), t Ruby, Python cho n PHP, C#, c th xem list ti y

Nhng m mnh recommend combo sau:

  • Ngn ng: JS/TS thn thin vi React Native dev

  • WebDriver client: WebdriverIO v trong m client, thng ny nhiu star trn github nht =))

  • Test library: jasmine
    • V n c c php ging Jest, m anh em code React Native th qu quen thuc vi Jest ri
    • L 1 trong 3 test framework c WebdriverIO support sn go pro =)) (ngoi ra cn c mocha v cucumber), dng Jest nu li th phi t my m thi :v

Nh ni trn, Appium p dng kin trc client-server. Khi ta vit nhng cu lnh sau

nu log ta c th thy nhng dng log di y, webdriverio ch n thun gi 1 HTTP request ti server, server lm g th chng ta s tm hiu sau :v

  • iOS
  • Android

3.2. Appium server, Automation tool, Devices

y l phn xng sng trong kin trc ca Appium, n m nhn vic handle request t client, giao tip vi native automation tool thc thi nhng command m ta cn.

Appium server expose ra API theo chun JSON Wire Protocol (WebDriver Protocol). Tu vo target l iOS hay Android, n s c cch hot ng ring ph hp vi nn tng .

3.2.1. Appium meets iOS

Quay tr li on log phn 3.1, n t nhiu gi cho ta cch hot ng ca Appium

C th d thy Appium server n gin ch proxy request ca ta ti 1 server khc chy port 8100 http://127.0.0.1:8100.

Ot d phc? Thng no ang chy port 8100 vy?

l WebDriverAgent server, ban u c pht trin bi ng ln Facebook, appium fork v thm mm thm mui g vo.

WDA gip giao tip vi XCUITest c th iu khin device/simulator iOS t xa. Bn thn n cng support sn Webdriver Protocol, vy nn chc hn dev Appium ngh nh sau

Ti g m phi code li, c sn hng ngon ri th dng lun thi =))

WDA lm g vi device th mnh xin skip, v cng ko bit =)) Cc bn c th t mnh tm hiu su hn nu c hng th vi n.

3.2.2. Appium meets Android

Vi Android, ta c t gi hn

Khng thy proxy g phi khng no? ng vy, v n c proxy u :v

version mi nht, Appium s dng appium-android-driver giao tip vi UIAutomator2. Vy giao tip th no?

Mi khi bt u chy test, Appium s ci app Appium Settings trn device ca ta, thng ny s m port 4724 trn device ca ta v expose ra mt vi API h thng. Appium server abc vi app ci trn (qua HTTP), v n s xyz vi UIAutomator2 thc hin cc command.

4. Kt lun

L mt dev, chng ta khng c ch quan, l thuc vo bn tester, m hy t mnh kim th trc khi chuyn qua cho h. Test chy cm l mt cng vic nhm chn, vy th ti sao chng ta khng lm cho n th v hn bng cch automate n. Tuy s c lc cn mt s th thut, hay l phi dng nhiu command kh lng nhng ( nh ci datepicker chng hn =)) ), nhng mt khi chy c nht nh n s em li cho cc bn mt cm gic ph nh con t t =))

Code e2e ca bi vit ch l nhng on code tm b, cc bn mun go pro c th tham kho appium-boilerplate ca webdriverio v cch chia module, cng nh setup project. Nu c thi gian mnh s vit thm v vic refactor ng code tm b trn go pro =)) Gi th xin tm bit cc bn.
